- [growls]

284
00:18:17.598 --> 00:18:18.640
[grunts]

285
00:18:27.065 --> 00:18:28.525
[growls]

286
00:18:30.027 --> 00:18:32.154
- [growls]
- [whimpers]

287
00:18:34.198 --> 00:18:35.616
