I can shut down the synaptic link.

305
00:19:40.389 --> 00:19:42.558
- I gotta go get Cate.
- No. Dr. Ran...

306
00:19:42.641 --> 00:19:44.226
- Wait. wait. wait. wait.
- What?

307
